data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Built in 2021, this stunning residence offers modern luxury and convenience. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, complemented by a 3-car garage for ample parking. The owner's suite boasts a private bath and walk-in closet, while the 2nd-floor laundry adds practicality. With 3 additional bedrooms, a 1st-floor study, sunroom and a full basement, space is abundant. Enjoy outdoor living in the privacy-fenced backyard with a stamped concrete patio and a charming front porch. Your perfect home awaits - schedule a viewing today!
